#### INSTALLATION and REQUIREMENTS 

Installing required software on RHEL/CentOS: 
    yum install php-cli php-mysql perl-Time-HiRes

Installing required software on Ubuntu/Debian: 
    apt-get install php-cli php-mysql perl-Time-HiRes

Then unzip, configure and run ./check_run.sh

#### CONFIGURATION 

- Edit email in check_run.sh where report will be sent
- Edit hostname AND MySQL credentials in check_run.sh if needed
